.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, emerald, ebony, white, black
There are 5 different nationalities: dutch, british, german, french, polish
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, vegafina, dannemann, pall-mall, game
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-7up, 7up, sprite, lemonade, fanta
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, pony, fish, snake

1. the dutch is the person who likes grey
2. the british is the owner of the rabbit
3. the person drinking iced-7up is the person who likes emerald
4. the german is the person drinking 7up
5. the person who likes emerald is to the right of the person who likes ebony
6. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the snake
7. the vegafina-smoker is the person who likes white
8. the person drinking sprite is in the middle
9. the french is on the far left
10. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle
11. the vegafina-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the fish
12. the pall-mall-smoker is the person drinking lemonade
13. the polish is the game-smoker
14. the french is to the left or right of the person who likes black

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   french	|    german	|     dutch	|    british	|    polish	|
| Color		|    white	|      black	|      grey	|     ebony	|     emerald	|
| Beverage	|     fanta	|      7up	|      sprite	| lemonade	|     iced-7up	|
| Cigar		|     vegafina	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| pall-mall	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     turtle	|     fish	|     snake	|     rabbit	|     pony	|
